OL,3,CThree more charged with murder after
OL,4,Cteen stabbed to death outside mosque
OL,6,FThree more people have been charged
OL,7,Fwith murder after a teenager was
OL,8,Fstabbed to death outside a mosque in
OL,9,FSmethwick.
OL,11,FZeshan Afzal was stabbed outside Jamia
OL,12,FMasjid, on Oldbury Road shortly before
OL,13,F9pm on 20 February.
OL,15,FTwo 18-year-olds, Aaman Khalil and
OL,16,FRehaan Siddique, and a 17-year-old
OL,17,Fboy, have been charged with murder.
OL,19,F10 teenagers had previously been
OL,20,Fcharged with murder following Zeshan's
OL,21,Fdeath.
