OL,3,CThree more charged with murder after
OL,4,Cteen stabbed to death outside mosque
OL,6,FThey were due to appear at Birmingham
OL,7,FMagistrates Court on Wednesday, July
OL,8,F15th.
OL,10,FA total of 13 people have now been
OL,11,Fcharged with murder as part of the
OL,12,FWest Midlands Police investigation.
OL,14,FThe force is still appealing for
OL,15,Finformation that could help officers
OL,16,Fwith enquiries.
